OL,3,CFormer Border Force officer jailed
OL,4,Cafter supplying MDMA
OL,6,FA former Border Force field
OL,7,Fintelligence officer has been jailed
OL,8,Fafter supplying MDMA.
OL,10,FGareth Glynn Davies, 44, of Cleves
OL,11,FWay, Ashford, Kent was arrested in
OL,12,FJanuary 2020.
OL,14,FFollowing the arrest, searches of his
OL,15,Fcar and home address led to the
OL,16,Frecovery of a lock knife, rambo knife,
OL,17,Fmachete, two knuckle dusters and a
OL,18,Fbaton.
