OL,3,CFormer Border Force officer jailed
OL,4,Cafter supplying MDMA
OL,6,FDavies, worked for Border Force at
OL,7,FFolkestone when he became the subject
OL,8,Fof an investigation after the NCA
OL,9,Freceived information that he may be
OL,10,Finvolved in drug supply.
OL,12,FHe was put under surveillance in late
OL,13,F2019. The investigation included the
OL,14,Fuse of surveillance and a range of
OL,15,Fundercover tactics.
OL,17,FOver the coming weeks, he had a number
OL,18,Fof meetings with a contact, who he
OL,19,Farranged to sell drugs to.
