OL,3,CFormer Border Force officer jailed
OL,4,Cafter supplying MDMA
OL,6,FOn 21 January 2020, he supplied four
OL,7,Fpills to the contact as a sample with
OL,8,Fthe promise of 5000 more. Following
OL,9,Fthe handover, Davies was arrested.
OL,11,FHe was subsequently charged with two
OL,12,Fdrug supply offences, and dismissed
OL,13,Ffrom his role at Border Force.
OL,15,FDavies pleaded guilty on 15 April 2024
OL,16,Fto both counts on the indictment. He
OL,17,Fwas sentenced at Maidstone Crown Court
OL,18,Ftoday (30 May 2024) to five years and
OL,19,F11 months.
