OL,4,Cafter supplying MDMA
OL,6,FDave Rock, from the NCA's Anti-
OL,7,FCorruption Unit, said: "It is a
OL,8,Fpriority for the NCA to tackle insider
OL,9,Fthreat and corruption at the border,
OL,10,Fand we work extremely closely with our
OL,11,Fcolleagues at Border Force every day
OL,12,Fto prevent illegal drugs entering the
OL,13,FUK.
OL,15,F"Davies thought he was beyond the
OL,16,Freach of the law, willingly disclosing
OL,17,Finformation that revealed his
OL,18,Fcriminality.
